{"tid":450051,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大家覺得公司服務有問題應唔應該鬧CS?","createTime":"2017-10-27T18:48:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-28T06:58:20.000Z","uid":62063,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"23d192cc65def9de981fd3c163bbad7ee218baa5","tid":450051,"uid":62063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T18:48:54.000Z","msg":"喺Facebook見到啲留意純粹有感而發<br />\n<br />\n渣打單嘢令好多炒家都不滿，仲唔少人話要打去鬧爆個CS。雖然香港投訴文化盛行，但喺香港大多數嘅投訴唔係理性要求解決方案，而係乜都唔理直接鬧serve你嗰個人。相信以上情況大家係社會中見怪不怪，造成咗一種唔太好嘅風氣。諗深一層，你將自己嘅憤怒發洩喺一個唔關佢事嘅人身上真係好咩。換轉大家係被遷怒嘅人會點諗，屌喇都唔關我事，無端端係咁俾人鬧。可能有人會覺得做得呢啲職位預咗俾人鬧，但我覺得如果改變社會風氣嘅話就唔係必然會發生嘅事。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/28/024823_ff8bbae0d05ebd998745ba4fefc1ba22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F28%2F024823_ff8bbae0d05ebd998745ba4fefc1ba22.jpg&h=f3242478&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/28/024824_5acc8bd7eafaaf1ecd4ca5417e590b36.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F28%2F024824_5acc8bd7eafaaf1ecd4ca5417e590b36.jpg&h=661a05d6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/28/024827_9dd257b0c64ef986ad42e2634b33e447.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F28%2F024827_9dd257b0c64ef986ad42e2634b33e447.jpg&h=0120c3e6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"74c73755e24a569505d450ae56e17bf02dc80f00","tid":450051,"uid":126479,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T18:51:31.000Z","msg":"公司問題係公司問題嘛<br />\n唔係cs問題，鬧cs個D都on9"},{"pid":"d8e6cbd3d8a542583378e7040741578f4dc7379c","tid":450051,"uid":33643,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T18:51:48.000Z","msg":"CS責任係處理客户投訴<br />\n但奈何香港好多西客投訴語氣過火，好尻乞人憎"},{"pid":"ab3611216a50072dc1a4137d8af801198d6c1a61","tid":450051,"uid":83201,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T19:10:44.000Z","msg":"但我覺得cs 就係個客同公司溝通嘅渠道，個客唔打去cs 鬧，可以點？如果話cut 左佢張卡打擊佢就算，咁一兩個客cut 冇用，依家見事去到咁揚，銀行先會肯處理，仲有依件事真係值得投訴，唔係為投訴而投訴<br />\n<br />\n利申：非苦主"},{"pid":"e59581b4928ee474655e1b2368e757eb46b5a19a","tid":450051,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T06:52:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88db29b99549a9a4c1a0b91fdc4a073eae09c72d","tid":450051,"uid":15921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T06:58:20.000Z","msg":"其實合理地鬧同埋唔好侮辱個cs，咁係可以接受<br />\n<br />\n利申：做緊cs"}]}